
This option saves the EGlib configuration in a file named "EG_LIB.CNF" which contains:
* all the EGlib parameters (options, fonts, memory size, screen size).
* all the form windows position.
* the position and historic of the online help window.

The file is read at the program start: all windows are opened and all the parameters are set automatically.

